Możecie to poczuć w sobie.

00:40:13.940 --> 00:40:15.960
On was słyszy.

00:40:15.960 --> 00:40:20.920
On was rozumie.

00:40:20.920 --> 00:40:29.300
On jest chwałą wszelkiej chwały.

00:40:29.420 --> 00:40:31.000
On was kocha.

00:40:33.420 --> 00:40:35.260
On was chroni.

00:40:35.400 --> 00:40:37.380
On was prowadzi.

00:40:37.380 --> 00:40:42.680
